
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I select 'Yes' radio button from Contrast enhanced box on Page 03 of Elbow MRI
And	I go to Page 07 of Elbow MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Neuritis' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Ulnar nerve' radio button is enabled
And 'Radial nerve' radio button is enabled
And 'Median nerve' radio button is enabled

And 'Hypertrophy' checkbox is enabled
And 'Surrounding fibrosis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Compression' checkbox is enabled
And 'Contrast enhancement' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Ulnar nerve' radio button
Then 'Dislocation' radio button is enabled
And 'Accessory anconeus epitrochlearis muscle' radio button is enabled
And 'Retinacular thickening' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Median nerve' radio button
Then 'Supracondylar process with ligament to medial epicondyle' radio button is enabled
Then 'Thickened bicipital aponeurosis' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Compression' checkbox
Then 'Ganglion/mass' radio button is enabled
And 'Adhesions' radio button is enabled
And 'Osteophytes' radio button is enabled
And 'Fracture' radio button is enabled
